# PriorityQueue&lt;T&gt;.Dequeue method

Removes and returns the smallest item from the [`PriorityQueue`](../PriorityQueue-1.md). This operation takes O(log n) time.

```csharp
public T Dequeue()
```

## Return Value

The smallest item in the [`PriorityQueue`](../PriorityQueue-1.md).
